Introduction

Jimin is a South Korean singer under M25.

On September 8, 2021, Jimin was revealed as a contestant on the MBC's survival show "My Teenage Girl". During the finale, she ranked first place with 243,302.4 votes, thus becoming the center of the girl group CLASS:y. CLASS:y made their debut on May 5, 2022 with the mini album "Class Is Over".

On January 14, 2024, Jimin was reported as one of the member of PocketDol Studio's collaboration group, A SIX. They released the digital single "Lies All Love" on January 30, 2024.
